e>p0\/\/3r-p0sT3r!</span><br> <font color=#000033>(11/27/01 11:23:20 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/feqasylumcleric.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=251.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Looking for info on Zordak Ragefire</span><hr size=1> There are many rumors, myths and superstions reguarding ragefire.  Let me tell it to you straight.  I personally watched 4 ragefires when camping him for my and discoved these things.<br>
<br>
Myth 1: His spawn is 0-72 hours in length. FALSE sat there for 80hours watching ( between me and roommates ) and he didn't spawn.<br>
<br>
Myth 2: After his first death he'll respawn 23-24 hours later. FALSE, he may not spawn again before the next naggy pop.<br>
<br>
Myth 3: You can calculate his spawn time based on Naggy/Magus's death. FALSE tried using the silly calculator thing on the cleric epic guide and it was flat our wrong.<br>
<br>
Basically, it's completely random.  There are really no two ways about it.  I wish you luck, for when he does pop, you can bet there will be feirce compation for him. <p><center><img src="http://merkabaeq.homestead.com/files/merkabasig.JPG"></center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#E5E5E6><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/ulittlecherub.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Little Cherub</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Cyber Pimp</span><br> <font color=#000033>(11/28/01 12:42:54 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/feqasylumcleric.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=251.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Looking for info on Zordak Ragefire</span><hr size=1> /nod Merkaba, it's just a game of patience and luck.<br>
